query:
SELECT DISTINCT 
  i.tenantId,
  COALESCE(t.name, 'OPERADOR LOGÍSTICO (NULL)') as dono_estoque,
  COUNT(*) as posicoes,
  SUM(i.quantity) as quantidade_total
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
GROUP BY i.tenantId, t.name;
